         Corto, I do see what your trying to say, but More HP does = More mana in a sense.  For example, lets say conversion rate is 2hp = 1 mana.  Character 1 has 1000 HP and character 2 has 2000 HP.. both have mana pool of 1000.  If both go oom, And they lich, character 1 will convert all his HP into 500 Mana, Character 2 will convert all his HP into 1000 Mana and he will be FM, while character 1 is still only 50% mana and has to regain some HP again to start lich again.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
