        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         My Int hovers around 205. Fully raid buffed I go over 3300hp.  I go for hp because I help heal, and I provide CC when possible.  A resisted ST puts you way up on the aggro list and I like to be able to take hits while I channel through another ST. In HoT I often have to stand inside the AoE to stay near the MT for healing, so once again hp save my butt from the damage.  <BR>I listened to the other necros here a while back when they said hp>all and I am a believer. :)</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=322613" target="_blank">Loreana Shahnra</a></P><P>60th Level Human Warlock of Innoruuk<BR>Tribunal</P><P>'The world is a scary place<BR>Now that you've woken up the demon in me'<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
